Package: blizzard-onbus
Section: net
Priority: optional
Depends: blizzard-rdk, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Blizzard Bus Bridge
 A unified bridge that exposes Blizzard SDK providers on various bus systems.
 Supports both RBus (rbus) and ubus with compile-time backend selection.
 .
 This package contains the bus bridge binary and init scripts.
